# Privacy Policy for Word Chain

**Effective Date:** [26.07.2025]  
**Last Updated:** [26.07.2025]

## Introduction

This Privacy Policy describes how Word Chain ("we," "our," or "us") collects, uses, and protects your information when you use our mobile application Word Chain (the "App"). We are committed to protecting your privacy and ensuring transparency about our data practices.

## Information We Collect

### Information You Provide
- **Game Progress Data**: Your game scores, daily challenge completions, word chains, and achievement progress
- **Language Preferences**: Your selected language for gameplay
- **In-App Purchase Information**: Purchase history and owned items (themes, power-ups)

### Information Automatically Collected
- **Device Information**: Device model, operating system version, unique device identifiers
- **Usage Analytics**: App usage patterns, feature usage, crash reports, and performance data
- **Advertising Data**: Information used to serve personalized advertisements

### Information from Third Parties
- **Google Play Services**: Account information if you sign in with Google Play Games
- **Advertising Partners**: Information from our advertising partners for ad personalization

## How We Use Your Information

We use the collected information for the following purposes:

### Core App Functionality
- Saving your game progress and settings
- Providing daily challenges and tracking completion
- Managing your inventory of purchased items
- Synchronizing data across devices (if applicable)

### App Improvement
- Analyzing app usage to improve features and user experience
- Identifying and fixing bugs and technical issues
- Developing new features and content

### Advertising
- Displaying relevant advertisements through Google AdMob
- Personalizing ad content based on your interests
- Measuring ad performance and effectiveness

### Legal and Safety
- Complying with legal obligations
- Protecting against fraud and abuse
- Enforcing our Terms of Service

## Data Sharing and Disclosure

We may share your information in the following circumstances:

### Service Providers
- **Google AdMob**: For displaying advertisements
- **Google Play Billing**: For processing in-app purchases
- **Analytics Services**: For app performance and usage analysis

### Legal Requirements
- When required by law or legal process
- To protect our rights, property, or safety
- To protect the rights, property, or safety of our users

### Business Transfers
- In connection with a merger, acquisition, or sale of assets

## Children's Privacy

Our app is designed to be family-friendly and may be used by children under 13. We take special care to protect children's privacy:

### COPPA Compliance
- We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13
- We do not use persistent identifiers to track children across apps or websites
- We do not serve behavioral advertising to children

### Parental Controls
- Parents can contact us to review, delete, or stop further collection of their child's information
- We encourage parents to monitor their children's app usage

## Your Rights and Choices

### Data Access and Control
- **Access**: Request access to your personal data
- **Correction**: Request correction of inaccurate data
- **Deletion**: Request deletion of your personal data
- **Portability**: Request a copy of your data in a portable format

### Advertising Choices
- **Opt-out**: You can opt out of personalized advertising through your device settings
- **Ad Settings**: Manage ad preferences through Google Ad Settings
- **Limit Ad Tracking**: Enable "Limit Ad Tracking" on iOS or "Opt out of Ads Personalization" on Android

### Account Deletion
- You can delete your game data by uninstalling the app
- Contact us to request complete data deletion from our servers

## Data Security

We implement appropriate security measures to protect your information:

### Technical Safeguards
- Encryption of data in transit and at rest
- Secure servers and databases
- Regular security assessments and updates

### Access Controls
- Limited access to personal data on a need-to-know basis
- Employee training on data protection practices
- Regular monitoring for unauthorized access

## Data Retention

We retain your information for as long as necessary to provide our services:

- **Game Data**: Retained while you use the app and for a reasonable period after
- **Analytics Data**: Typically retained for 2-3 years for analysis purposes
- **Legal Requirements**: Some data may be retained longer to comply with legal obligations

## International Data Transfers

Your information may be transferred to and processed in countries other than your own. We ensure appropriate safeguards are in place for such transfers in compliance with applicable data protection laws.

## Third-Party Services

Our app integrates with third-party services that have their own privacy policies:

- **Google AdMob**: [Google Privacy Policy](https://policies.google.com/privacy)
- **Google Play Services**: [Google Privacy Policy](https://policies.google.com/privacy)
- **Google Play Billing**: [Google Privacy Policy](https://policies.google.com/privacy)

## Changes to This Privacy Policy

We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any material changes by:
- Posting the updated policy in the app
- Updating the "Last Updated" date
- Providing notice through the app or other means

## Contact Us

